== Caanaha Xoolaha ==
Mid ka mid ah litir oo caano lo'aad oo caadi ah ee cayriin (la daaweyn) ka kooban yahay celcelis ahaan ku saabsan 32-40 g borotiinada, oo ay ku jiraan casein (cheese) borotiinada qiyaastii 30 g of Alfa-lactalbumin 1.4 g of beta-lactoglobulin 3.3 g, immunoglobulins 0.7 g, glycomacropeptide qiyaastii 1 g, iyo 0.1 g of lactoferrin. Lisay inta lagu jiro dhalmada dhowr maalmood ka dib in content protein caanaha waa gaar sare. Caanaha noocan oo kale ah waxa loo yaqaan dambar. sida (Borotiinada Milk ) ayaa sidoo kale waxaa ka mid ah antimicrobials, falgalka sida lysozymes iyo lactoperoxidase, iyo arrimo koritaanka.Content Fat ee caanaha lo'da cayriin ee, Status waxa loogu yeero caano kala duwan tartanka lo'da ee model xilli ciyaareedkan iyo lo'da cuno cuntada. Celcelis ahaan, waa ku dhawaad ​​44 g / litir oo [8], galactosemic content ah lactose ee 48 g / litir. Caanaha Macdanta qiyaastii waa 7 garaam halkii litir [9]. Osteoporosis Federation of caanaha sida mid ka mid ah ilaha ugu wacan ee calcium cuntada somaligaa, oo waxay u soo jeedinay in ay xoog lafaha iyo dayactirka xaalad ka mid ah lafaha .Ee Hooyada iyo lo'da ka kooban baruurta caano kala duwan ka badan ay ka kooban protein. Isbeddelada ku dufanka cuntada hooyada saamayn profile acid dufanka leh caanaha. Cow ee kolestaroolka caanaha waa ka badan yihiin caanaha aadanaha. Baruurta caanaha Bovine ka kooban yahay ku dhawaad ​​53% acids cokan dufanka leh .
Processing ee caanaha 

Processing warshadaha oo caano ah meel dairies. Kala duwan ka soo caanaha laga soo tuuray meer isu soo wada qaso, kulaylka-daweeyey yareeyo bakteeriyada (pasteurization) ama jeermiska (UHT) daaweynta. Oo xaydha laga soocay separator ah. Qaar ka mid ah buttermilk baruurta inay subagga, waxaa loo isticmaalaa in soo saaridda ee farmaajo iyo qaar ka mid ah ku soo laabtay wax soo saarka caanaha dareeraha ah. Finland cream rasvapallomembraanit dillaaceen yar globules baruurta, oo sidaas daraaddeed, homogenization, halkaas oo baruurtii waa siman isku qasan oo leh caanaha. Dalalka oo dhan homogenisation waxaa laga codsadaa in kariimka sabayn dushiisa oo caano ah. Qaar ka mid ah kariimka waxaa ku soo laabtay caanaha. Waqtigan xaadirka ah, vitamin D lagu daraa caano inay hagaajiso qaadashada.

Iibiyo caanaha dukaan baruurta-buuxa oo ay ku jiraan ku dhowaad fiirsashada la mid ah sida caanaha lo'da ee asalka ahaa. Light In caanaha, baruurta iyo caano aan baruurta, ku dhawaad ​​kulli xaydhii laga saaray.

